es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.util

Class AdjacencyMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.util.AdjacencyMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class AdjacencyMap
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class implements a builder for calculating the adjacency map of an Octomap. Currenty ocotmap does not support querying for cells which are adjacent to others, so it is needed to implement an external tool to calculate and query that. It is important to recalculate the adjacency of the cells if the geometry of the map changes (new cells added, or the size of the cells changes).
    Since:
    09/03/2016
    Author:
    Adrián González Sieira <adrian.gonzalez@usc.es>

      private AdjacencyMap(JOctree octree)
